    <title>Joyful</title>
    <link href="https://hcy-08.github.io/2022/04/23/Joyful/"/>
    <id>https://hcy-08.github.io/2022/04/23/Joyful/</id>
    <published>2022-04-22T18:16:17.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-04-23T16:14:15.515Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Blog-Settings"><a href="#Blog-Settings" class="headerlink" title="Blog Settings"></a>Blog Settings</h1><p>今天把主題更換為 Next，跟 Apollo 比起來功能多上許多，介面同樣十分簡潔<br>邊看 <code>_config.yml</code> 邊熟悉各項客製化設定<br>目前打算施工的部分有：</p><h3 id="1-外觀"><a href="#1-外觀" class="headerlink" title="1. 外觀"></a>1. 外觀</h3><ul><li>Markdown 在 darkmode 下保持暗色</li><li>首頁文章標題、日期、內文、背景等配色</li><li>Markdown 程式語言配色</li><li>首頁放 logo，sidebar 的 logo 外框拿掉</li><li>文章放上預覽圖</li></ul><h3 id="2-功能"><a href="#2-功能" class="headerlink" title="2. 功能"></a>2. 功能</h3><ul><li>尚未閱讀完 Next docs，目前先從外觀著手</li><li>未來拓展不同文章分類，也許會以路由實現?</li></ul><h3 id="3-Bug"><a href="#3-Bug" class="headerlink" title="3. Bug"></a>3. Bug</h3><ul><li>sidebar 的 顯示錯誤，如下圖<br><img src="/../img/Joy-p1.png"></li></ul><hr><h1 id="Coding"><a href="#Coding" class="headerlink" title="Coding"></a>Coding</h1><h3 id="JS-與-HTML-的網頁練習"><a href="#JS-與-HTML-的網頁練習" class="headerlink" title="JS 與 HTML 的網頁練習"></a>JS 與 HTML 的網頁練習</h3><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">const</span> userInput = <span class="variable language_">document</span>.<span class="title function_">querySelector</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;#input-number&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">const</span> cBtn = <span class="variable language_">document</span>.<span class="title function_">querySelector</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;#btn-c&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">const</span> fBtn = <span class="variable language_">document</span>.<span class="title function_">querySelector</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;#btn-f&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">const</span> currentCalculation = <span class="variable language_">document</span>.<span class="title function_">querySelector</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;#current-calculation&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// Change the input type from string to float</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">const</span> <span class="title function_">getUserInput</span> = (<span class="params"></span>) =&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="built_in">parseFloat</span>(userInput.<span class="property">value</span>);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">const</span> <span class="title function_">c2f</span> = (<span class="params"></span>) =&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">const</span> enteredInput = <span class="title function_">getUserInput</span>().<span class="title function_">toFixed</span>(<span class="number">2</span>);</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">// console.log(&#x27;enteredInput&#x27;, enteredInput);</span></span><br><span class="line">  result = ((enteredInput * <span class="number">9</span>) / <span class="number">5</span> + <span class="number">32</span>).<span class="title function_">toFixed</span>(<span class="number">2</span>);</span><br><span class="line">  currentCalculation.<span class="property">textContent</span> = <span class="string">`<span class="subst">$&#123;enteredInput&#125;</span> C = <span class="subst">$&#123;result&#125;</span> F`</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">const</span> <span class="title function_">f2c</span> = (<span class="params"></span>) =&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">const</span> enteredInput = <span class="title function_">getUserInput</span>().<span class="title function_">toFixed</span>(<span class="number">2</span>);</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">// console.log(&#x27;enteredInput&#x27;, enteredInput);</span></span><br><span class="line">  result = (((enteredInput - <span class="number">32</span>) * <span class="number">5</span>) / <span class="number">9</span>).<span class="title function_">toFixed</span>(<span class="number">2</span>);</span><br><span class="line">  currentCalculation.<span class="property">textContent</span> = <span class="string">`<span class="subst">$&#123;enteredInput&#125;</span> F = <span class="subst">$&#123;result&#125;</span> C`</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">cBtn.<span class="title function_">addEventListener</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;click&#x27;</span>, c2f);</span><br><span class="line">fBtn.<span class="title function_">addEventListener</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;click&#x27;</span>, f2c);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如上面的 Code 所示，先宣告變數，從 HTML 取得不同 id 的資料<br>取得的 input 資料為 string，需要轉換成自己需要的 type<br>按鈕元件加上監聽，並觸發函數<br>輸出的區塊使用 <code>.textContent</code> 改變文字內容</p><p>這些概念不難，沒有牽扯到邏輯，資料結構或是演算法<br>但是 JS 與 HTML 的抓取資料與語法是目前我還需要熟悉的方向<br>以下整理重點：</p><ol><li>需要的 HTML 區塊，JS 宣告變數連結，前綴 id 用 <code>#</code>，class 用 <code>.</code></li><li>取得 Input 資料的區塊與 Output 的區塊</li><li>監聽觸發函數</li></ol><hr><h1 id="Adventure"><a href="#Adventure" class="headerlink" title="Adventure"></a>Adventure</h1><h3 id="松山-蔦居-自煮生活"><a href="#松山-蔦居-自煮生活" class="headerlink" title="松山 蔦居 自煮生活"></a>松山 蔦居 自煮生活</h3><p><img src="/../img/Joy-p2.jpg"></p><p>來到這裡喝了冰拿鐵與吃了手工乳酪蛋糕，以後書店想看的書可以帶進去好好看<br>冬天再來這裡喝手刷奶茶</p><hr><h1 id="Emotion-Notes"><a href="#Emotion-Notes" class="headerlink" title="Emotion Notes"></a>Emotion Notes</h1><p>從禮拜二開始，我已經保持了五天的愉快<br>不是嗑藥般短暫的愉悅，也不像過去建立在悲傷內核的表層快樂<br>而是從心底產生的愉快<br>有時淡有時濃烈，但是都使我精神極好，保持清醒</p><p>以前保持清醒的方式，就是不斷地看著過去，增強不甘，激發憤怒<br>我會進入憤怒但也同時很冷靜的狀態，做事效率顯著提高<br>缺點是持續不久，狀態結束後會反噬<br>長久下來，效率其實是極低的</p><p>撇開做事層面，我保持愉快的狀態，可以用像正常人的平常心，去面對一切問題<br>沒有預期的反饋?<br>意料之外的突發狀況?<br>甚至是遇到不愉快的事?<br>這些不都是人生的一部份，我可以選擇陷入悲傷迴圈，或是選擇接受，或是享受<br>漸漸的每件事，都撼動不了我的中心</p><p>我相信歸類成正能量與負能量是有道理存在的<br>悲傷，空虛與衍生情緒，都是低階的內耗，最終是和自己過不去<br>希望愉快能保持，並持續成長，不論遇到任何會摧毀脆弱時期自己的情緒與事件<br>我都能夠站穩，微笑以對，吸取養分</p><p>- HCY 2022&#x2F;04&#x2F;23</p>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">Keeping my joy</summary>
    
    
    
    
